{"type":"text","timestamp":1775902354702,"sessionID":"ses_283ffa16affeyiZ24apvNnRQcH","part":{"id":"prt_d7c0754ad001Co2665fgpwTqkq","messageID":"msg_d7c073b46001OUjpPWJjhdwJfj","sessionID":"ses_283ffa16affeyiZ24apvNnRQcH","type":"text","text":"The `proposal.md` for AR-027 has been written successfully. \n\nThe proposal includes all required sections:\n\n| Section | Content |\n|---------|---------|\n| **Purpose** | High-level SDK for Code Interpreter sessions and Agent Runtime workloads |\n| **Scope** | 8 In-Scope items (CodeInterpreterClient, AgentRuntimeClient, ControlPlaneClient, data plane clients, utilities, exceptions) and 10 Out-of-Scope items |\n| **Design** | Architecture diagrams, class structures, HTTP endpoint mappings, exception hierarchy |\n| **Impact Analysis** | Affected components, package dependencies, configuration resolution, timeout behavior, error scenarios |\n| **Alternatives Considered** | 7 alternatives with rejection rationale (single client class, asyncio-first, Pydantic, OpenAPI generation, unified config, tenacity retries, httpx) |\n| **Verification** | 4 code examples for client usage, error handling, direct client usage, and environment configuration |\n| **References** | Links to design docs, specs, and related ARs |\n| **Success Criteria** | 24 specific criteria for implementation verification |","time":{"start":1775902354699,"end":1775902354699}}}
